abstract: NFL Roundup; Seattle Seahawks running back Marshawn Lynch, who has missed past eight games because of abdominal injury, takes field for practice, but coach Pete Carroll gives no indication whether he will play in upcoming playoff game against Carolina Panthers; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Coach Pete Carroll cautioned that Lynch’s practicing was no indication about whether he would play in an N.F.C. divisional playoff game at Carolina on Sunday.

headline.main: Marshawn Lynch Practices, but the Seahawks Aren’t Sure He’ll Play
headline.print_headline: Lynch Practices, but the Seahawks Aren’t Sure He’ll Play
